<Event TYPE="Contact" SUBTYPE="Meet">Dinner</Event>.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-23" start="1954" end="2046">Not surprisingly, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER">Brokaw</ENAMEX> is listed on the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER">Fasulo</ENAMEX> book jacket as
