<ENAMEX TYPE="PER">Barbara Crossette</ENAMEX>, <Event TYPE="Personnel" SUBTYPE="End-Position">former</Event> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">New York Times</ENAMEX> bureau chief at the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">U.N</ENAMEX>. who
