<Event TYPE="Conflict" SUBTYPE="Attack">genocide</Event>.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-30" start="3001" end="3323">Writer and author <ENAMEX TYPE="PER">Philip Gourevitch</ENAMEX> has described in detail
