offered to help <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">U.N</ENAMEX>. forces in raiding the government stockpiles to be
used in the <Event TYPE="Conflict" SUBTYPE="Attack">genocide</Event> campaign.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-32" start="3439" end="3522">All that the informant wanted in return
