authorization to conduct such a raid and save lives.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-34" start="3603" end="3709">He asked for that
approval but the answer came back in a now-infamous &quot;genocide <Event TYPE="Contact" SUBTYPE="Phone-Write">fax</Event>&quot; from
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER">Annan</ENAMEX>&apos;s office.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-35" start="3709" end="3899">It denied authorization for the mission and told him
